  <section id="andre" class="team-member <%= @member != 'andre' ? 'hidden' : '' %>">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1>André Santos</h1>
      <h2>Systems Administrator</h2>

      <p>Mostly due to his Perl and bash skills, he expects his tombstone to read "Here lies the ultimate command-line ninja".</p>
      <p>A firm believer in the Open Source software philosophy, his role in Group Buddies is to manage a flock of servers which host the team's ideas.</p>
      <p>Apart from going into the Matrix, he enjoys practicing judo and backpacking around the world.</p>

      <a href="#" class="right arrow"></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="hugo" class="team-member <%= @member != 'hugo' ? 'hidden' : '' %>">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1>Hugo Marinho</h1>
      <h2>Software Developer</h2>

      <p>Started off doing freelance development and graphics design at a young age, now focusing more on Web Development.</p>
      <p>With an appetite for new challenges, he found in Group Buddies the opportunity to take on different projects with a talented team.</p>
      <p>Loves practicing Taekwondo and entertaining his neighbors with his dubious guitar playing. Amps to 11.</p>

      <a href="#" class="left arrow"></a>
      <a href="#" class="right arrow"></a>
    </div>
